1. *Drugačija* od svih ostalih (adjective position) (Different from all the others)
2. Ona ima *drugačiji* pogled na svijet (adjective position) (She has a different view of the world)
3. Ja ne volim taj film, meni se čini da je previše *drugačiji* od knjige (adjective position) (I don't like that movie, it seems too different from the book to me)
4. Mi smo *drugačiji* od drugih timova (predicate adjective) (We are different from the other teams)
5. Njena razmišljanja su potpuno *drugačija* od mojih (predicate adjective) (Her thoughts are completely different from mine)
6. Oni su navikli na *drugačiji* način života (adverb position) (They are accustomed to a different way of life)
7. Ja bih *drugačije* uradio da sam na tvom mjestu (adverb position) (I would do it differently if I were in your place)
8. *Drugačije* rečeno, to znači da ne možemo to učiniti (adverb position) (In other words, that means we can't do it)
9. Kada sam videla koliko je sve *drugačije* u Japanu, bila sam oduševljena (neuter gender singular form) (When I saw how everything is different in Japan, I was amazed)
10. Mnogo ljudi ne voli da proba nešto *drugačije* (neuter gender singular form) (Many people don't like to try something different)